dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:13:19.000Z","msg":"The Nobel Peace Prize 2017 was awarded to International Campaign to Abolish Nuclear Weapons (ICAN) &quot;for its work to draw attention to the catastrophic humanitarian consequences of any use of nuclear weapons and for its ground-breaking efforts to achieve a treaty-based prohibition of such weapons.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:14:56.000Z","msg":"Alongside serving as Director of the Acronym Institute, Rebecca is Co-Chair of theInternational Campaign to Abolish Nuclear Weapons (ICAN), Vice-President of theCampaign for Nuclear Disarmament (UK), and a member of the International Panel on Fissile Materials (IPFM), and the women&rsquo;s advisory group for the International Action Network on Small Arms (IANSA).<br />\n<br />\n自膠"},{"pid":"60789f48121a66a778593cbab49ebf10710c332b","tid":1262031,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770f12c4671b0630816341d0b9065cf2f0bb2a3c","tid":1262031,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:26:56.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"23229fd29deafda383c275df750704e5c011b1a0","tid":1262031,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T09:28:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}